properties.template:
[% MACRO wg_fb(objects) BLOCK %] [% tab_count = 0 %] [% FOREACH obj IN objects %] [% IF obj.isTabset %] [% wg_fb_tabset( obj ) %] [% ELSIF obj.isFieldset %] [% wg_fb_fieldset( obj ) %] [% ELSIF obj.field %] [% obj.field %] [% END %] [% END %] [% END %] [% MACRO wg_fb_tabset(tabset) BLOCK %]
    [% set_count = tab_count %] [% FOREACH tab IN tabset.tabs %] [% set_count = set_count + 1 %] [% tab.label %] [% END %]
[% set_count = tab_count %] [% FOREACH tab IN tabset.tabs %] [% set_count = set_count + 1 %]
[% wg_fb( tab.objects ) %]
[% END %]
[% tab_count = tab_count + set_count %]
[% END %] [% MACRO wg_fb_fieldset(fieldset) BLOCK %]
[% fieldset.label %] [% wg_fb( fieldset.objects ) %]
[% END %]
[% FOR error IN errors %]
[% error %]
[% END %] [% form_header %] [% wg_fb( form_objects ) %] [% form_footer %]
